strings.Value: "I hope she didn't ruin the day for you."
"Don't mention it. Well, I won't bother you anymore..."
"It's better than standing quiet, doing nothing."
"I didn't know Ntavi became a priestess. She changed a lot..." {n}Ekun frowns and wipes his brow.{/n} "Thanks for the help."
"This wasn't needed. But we couldn't stop it." {n}Ekun winces.{/n} "Come talk to me in a few days. I need to speak to you."
{n}Ekun looks away, feigning indifference.{/n} "Come talk to me in a few days. I need to speak to you."
"Come talk to me in a few days. I need to speak to you."
